{
  "texts": [
    "So far, raters in our studies were not aware of the source of the reappraisal.",
    "Given recent findings (Rubin et al., 2025; Yin et al., 2024), we were interested in examining the impact of labeling on quality, and whether such labeling reduced or even reversed the gap between human and GPT-4 reappraisals.",
    "EXPLORING HUMAN AND AI EMOTIONAL SUPPORT participants viewed vignette-reappraisal pairs in the same manner as the previous two study's raters, or a label condition, where participants viewed the same vignette-reappraisal pairs, but with the added label of whether the reappraisal came from human participants or GPT.",
    "The label was presented in bold right before the reappraisal to make sure that participants understood the source of reappraisal.",
    "The human reappraisals were taken from the full set of reappraisals generated by the participants in the condition without incentives in Study 3."
  ]
}